/wyroznienie-milestone-dla-polskich-matematykow-za-zlamanie-enigmy,artykuly,345107,1.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="IEEE">{{citation |first=Janina |last=Mazierska |title=IEEE Milestone Dedication on the First Breaking of Enigma Code (Poland Section) |journal=The IEEE Region 10 Newsletter |url=http://www.ieeer10.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IEEE-R10-Newsletter_Dec2014.pdf |date=December 2014 |pages=2–4 |accessdate=1 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227211412/http://www.ieeer10.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IEEE-R10-Newsletter_Dec2014.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
